text: Mohamed Adli Roushdi (21 July 1921 - 28 April 2016) was an Egyptian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Egyptian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
